"{\"uid\": \"express.co.uk-sport-othersport-1932212-2024-Olympics-gymnastics-Simone-Biles-medal\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  Simone Biles missed out on winning a fourth gold medal at the2024 Paris Olympicsafter making a critical mistake in the women's balance beam final.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 148, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The American slipped off the apparatus midway through her routine, with her eventual score of 13.100 only enough for fifth place.\", \"from\": 149, \"to\": 278, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 153, \"end\": 161, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999954951682926, \"rank\": 3.976556802878928e-06, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And the 27-year-old appeared irate afterwards, seemingly complaining about the crowd noise during her routine.\", \"from\": 280, \"to\": 390, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Prior to her slipping, shouts of \\\"come on Simone!\\\"\", \"from\": 392, \"to\": 442, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"could be heard, with other spectators reacting by trying to quieten those people down.\", \"from\": 443, \"to\": 529, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Biles said: \\\"Why are they (fans) shushing?\", \"from\": 531, \"to\": 573, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As soon as I am going, they are shushing so much.\", \"from\": 574, \"to\": 623, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's just annoying that the crowd also has to start shushing.\\\"\", \"from\": 624, \"to\": 686, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Her frustration was noted by Craig Heap on BBC commentary, who said: \\\"I have never seen Simone Biles so angry in my life.\", \"from\": 688, \"to\": 809, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 717, \"end\": 727, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Craig_Heap\", \"score\": 0.9999999999968168, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Craig Heap\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Craig_Heap\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Craig_Heap\"}, {\"begin\": 731, \"end\": 734, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\", \"score\": 0.7528700058239641, \"rank\": 0.3276769229571516, \"text\": \"BBC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Something has gone on there.\", \"from\": 810, \"to\": 838, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"She is not happy at all.\", \"from\": 840, \"to\": 865, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It just goes to show she is a human being.\", \"from\": 866, \"to\": 908, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"All the other ladies in that final have made mistakes.\", \"from\": 909, \"to\": 963, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She's not invincible.\\\"\", \"from\": 964, \"to\": 986, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Fellow American Sunisa Lee explained: \\\"The crowd shushing us for cheering, we did not like that because it was just so silent in there.\", \"from\": 988, \"to\": 1123, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 988, \"end\": 994, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Institute_of_Electrical_and_Electronics_Engineers\", \"score\": 0.9324850150505972, \"rank\": 0.05190061556636463, \"text\": \"Fellow\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Institute_of_Electrical_and_Electronics_Engineers\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Institute_of_Electrical_and_Electronics_Engineers\"}, {\"begin\": 995, \"end\": 1003, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999954951682926, \"rank\": 3.976556802878928e-06, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 1004, \"end\": 1014, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sunisa_Lee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sunisa Lee\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sunisa_Lee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sunisa_Lee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I love hearing my teammates cheer for me.\", \"from\": 1124, \"to\": 1165, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"That's not how I wanted to end my Olympic games, and I am sure she did not want that either.\", \"from\": 1167, \"to\": 1260, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We were just talking about how annoying it was to be shushed.\", \"from\": 1262, \"to\": 1324, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We were just both really upset.\\\"\", \"from\": 1325, \"to\": 1357, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Discovery+is the new home of the Olympics.\", \"from\": 1361, \"to\": 1403, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The streamer is set to broadcast 3,800 hours of sport live from Paris.\", \"from\": 1404, \"to\": 1474, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1468, \"end\": 1473, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999973956619, \"rank\": 2.6041574863325637e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sports fans can getDiscovery+ for \\u00a33.99a month until the end of 2024 via Amazon Prime's video channels.\", \"from\": 1476, \"to\": 1579, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1549, \"end\": 1561, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_Prime\", \"score\": 0.9934200430579532, \"rank\": 0.006623539455142821, \"text\": \"Amazon Prime\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_Prime\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_Prime\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This also comes with anAmazon Prime 30-day free trial.\", \"from\": 1580, \"to\": 1634, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Biles appeared to have made a strong and composed start to her routine.\", \"from\": 1636, \"to\": 1707, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But as she executed a 'double layout', the USA icon with 10 Olympic medals to her name stumbled and was unable to keep her footing.\", \"from\": 1708, \"to\": 1839, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1751, \"end\": 1754, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9912820871121183, \"rank\": 0.006902307263722603, \"text\": \"USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As she waited for her score, Biles was agitated further as camera crews got close to her.\", \"from\": 1841, \"to\": 1930, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She then entered into a deep discussion with her coach after finding out she could not win a medal.\", \"from\": 1931, \"to\": 2030, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And straight after the competition, she headed straight for the backstage area.\", \"from\": 2032, \"to\": 2111, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She now has just over an hour before going for gold again in the individual floor final.\", \"from\": 2112, \"to\": 2200, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It was Italian Alice D'Amato, 21, who took gold despite only qualifying as seventh best.\", \"from\": 2202, \"to\": 2290, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2209, \"end\": 2216, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_language\", \"score\": 0.9830058871166607, \"rank\": 0.015857435304738102, \"text\": \"Italian\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_language\"}, {\"begin\": 2217, \"end\": 2230, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alice_D'Amato\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Alice D'Amato\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alice_D'Amato\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alice_D'Amato\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her score of 14.366 was enough to beat silver medalist Zhou Yaqin, of China, while another Italian in Manila Esposito took bronze.\", \"from\": 2291, \"to\": 2421, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2346, \"end\": 2350, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zhou_Enlai\", \"score\": 0.8808491102980327, \"rank\": 0.12609495112802166, \"text\": \"Zhou\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zhou_Enlai\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zhou_Enlai\"}, {\"begin\": 2351, \"end\": 2356, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yaqeen\", \"score\": 0.9999999999818101, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Yaqin\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yaqeen\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yaqeen\"}, {\"begin\": 2393, \"end\": 2399, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Manila\", \"score\": 0.9991058313027442, \"rank\": 0.0008936051750948558, \"text\": \"Manila\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Manila\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Manila\"}, {\"begin\": 2400, \"end\": 2408, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phil_Esposito\", \"score\": 0.9989222923641842, \"rank\": 0.0010788702388143199, \"text\": \"Esposito\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q11774891\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phil_Esposito\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phil_Esposito\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We use your sign-up to provide content in ways you have consented to and to improve our understanding of you.\", \"from\": 2423, \"to\": 2532, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This may include adverts from us and 3rd parties based on our understanding.\", \"from\": 2533, \"to\": 2609, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can unsubscribe at any time.\", \"from\": 2610, \"to\": 2642, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy Policy  D'Amato burst into tears when her gold medal was confirmed.\", \"from\": 2643, \"to\": 2726, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But for Biles, the beam event continues to elude her in her illustrious Olympic career.\", \"from\": 2727, \"to\": 2814, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She already has three gold medals to her name in Paris, and seven overall.\", \"from\": 2816, \"to\": 2890, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2865, \"end\": 2870, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999973956619, \"rank\": 2.6041574863325637e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But she only won bronze in that discipline in Rio in 2016, and had the same result in Tokyo five years later.\", \"from\": 2891, \"to\": 3000, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2937, \"end\": 2940, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999998561138558, \"rank\": 1.438861157250691e-07, \"text\": \"Rio\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 2977, \"end\": 2982, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.999861763164958, \"rank\": 0.00013825354665914123, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"SEARCH  CONNECT WITH US  TODAY'S PAPER  See today's front and back pages, download the newspaper, order back issues and use the historic Daily Express newspaper archive.\", \"from\": 3002, \"to\": 3171, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3139, \"end\": 3152, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.06360013327415e-20, \"text\": \"Daily Express\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q23446